STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Christopher B. FOUNTAIN, a/k/a Buck Fountain, Chris Fountain and Charles M. Spivey, Defendant-Petitioner. C-496 September Term 2018
081465 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 18, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004321-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
